message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm pleased with the service I've received so far. I just have a quick question about my policy.
That's great to hear! I'd be happy to help. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security?
Of course, my full name is Sarah Johnson.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. How can I assist you with your policy query?
I wanted to inquire about adding extra coverage to my current policy. Is that something you can help me with?
Absolutely, Sarah. A possible resolution could be reviewing our available add-ons for your policy. Would you like me to present some options?
Yes, please. I'm open to exploring additional coverage options.
Great! Let me run through some choices with you. How about adding comprehensive roadside assistance for your vehicle? Does this work for you?
That sounds like a good option for me. Thank you for suggesting that.
I'm glad we could help. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Sarah?
No, Chris, that's all sorted for now. Thank you for your assistance.
You're welcome, Sarah. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
